<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="page-hero" style="background:var(--white); padding-top:140px; padding-bottom:60px; text-align:center;">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 style="color:var(--text-dark); margin-bottom:16px;">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--text-muted); font-size:1.1rem;">How we handle and protect your data.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section" style="padding: 60px 0; background:var(--bg-gray);">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:800px; background:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); backdrop-filter:blur(16px); padding:40px; border-radius:var(--radius); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03), inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);">
    
    <h2 style="font-size:1.4rem; margin-bottom:12px; margin-top:24px; color:var(--text-dark);">1. Introduction</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.8;">At D Cyber Office, your privacy is a top priority. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information we collect from our clients, how we use it, and the measures we take to keep it secure.</p>
    
    <h2 style="font-size:1.4rem; margin-bottom:12px; margin-top:24px; color:var(--text-dark);">2. Information Collection</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.8;">We may collect personal identification information (Name, Email Address, Phone Number) when you use our website or contact us for services. As a healthcare BPO, we also process Patient Health Information (PHI) under strict compliance with HIPAA (please see our <a href="/hipaa" style="color:var(--primary); text-decoration:underline;">HIPAA Notice</a>).</p>
    
    <h2 style="font-size:1.4rem; margin-bottom:12px; margin-top:24px; color:var(--text-dark);">3. Information Use</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.8;">The information we collect is used to:</p>
    <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom:20px; line-height:1.8; color:var(--text-muted);">
      <li>Provide, operate, and maintain our BPO services.</li>
      <li>Process healthcare claims and medical billing operations securely.</li>
      <li>Communicate with you regarding service updates or inquiries.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.4rem; margin-bottom:12px; margin-top:24px; color:var(--text-dark);">4. Data Protection and Security</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.8;">We implement advanced security measures including encryption, secure servers, and strict access controls to maintain the safety of your personal information and any PHI we handle on your behalf.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.4rem; margin-bottom:12px; margin-top:24px; color:var(--text-dark);">5. Third-Party Disclosure</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.8;">We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer to outside parties your personally identifiable information unless we provide you with advance notice, or as required by law to process medical claims and billing through authorized clearinghouses and insurance providers.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.4rem; margin-bottom:12px; margin-top:24px; color:var(--text-dark);">6. Contact Us</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.8;">If there are any questions regarding this privacy policy, you may contact us using the information on our <a href="/contact" style="color:var(--primary); text-decoration:underline;">Contact Page</a>.</p>

  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
